sentences: In 1954 Chiyoko won the 1st prize of the Columbia Music Entertainment singers competition.
In 1955, she made her recording début with the single "Konoyo no Hana".
However, she forgot her song lyrics in 1996.
She participated again in the Kohaku in 2004.
After a long battle with liver cancer, she died, at age 75, on 8 November 2013.
